The parcels of land covered by this proclamation contain an aggregate of NINETY THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED THIRTY SEVEN (90,937) SQUARE METERS.

The Department of Environment and Natural Resources is hereby authorized to issue the Special Patent in favor of the City Government of Olongapo covering the parcels of land subject of this Proclamation, provided that the same are subject to recall when public interest and welfare so demand.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 5th day of August , Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

